data.description: This home is located in the highly desirable Kingswood neighborhood on one of the largest treed lots, it backs up to a peaceful creek and greenbelt. Vaulted ceilings in the living room and a huge bonus room in the back. Private Carport in the back. Huge backyard with workshop with electricity, refrigerator and ac. Sprinkler system for front and back yard. Boat shed with electricity. Back yard has several seating areas and plenty of birds to watch and listen to. Roof was replaced in July 2023. Easy access to highway and Joe Pool Lake. Home is for sale due to divorce. Make this house your home today! Great opportunity, Current 3.125% loan is assumable with Lakeview Mtg.
